headline: New Report from Intuit Mailchimp Shows Most Marketers are Using AI, Highlights Differentiators For Top Performers
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., November 12, 2024--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, today shares its latest report, "The Revenue Blueprint: Strategies for Performance-Obsessed Marketers." headline: Intuit (INTU) Slipped on Slower Growth Outlook
summary: Baron Funds, an investment management company, released its “Baron FinTech Fund” third quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the third quarter, the fund rose 12.52% (Institutional Shares) compared to a 12.21% return for the FactSet Global FinTech Index (Benchmark) and a 5.89% gain for the S&P 500 […]
